# Robot Kinematics

## Description

This package contains a ROS2 node that reads the velocities of two differential wheels and recalculates the position of the robot.

## Installation

1. Clone the repository into your ROS2 workspace:
    ```sh
    cd ~/ros2_ws/src
    git clone <repository_url> robot_kinematics
    ```

2. Build the package:
    ```sh
    cd ~/ros2_ws
    colcon build
    ```

3. Source the workspace:
    ```sh
    source ~/ros2_ws/install/setup.bash
    ```

